WRITING.TITLE: [REVIEW] 1k Haul Part 2!
WRITING.TEXT:
#INTRODUCTION Part 2 is here, sorry it took so long but I missed 2 parcels whilst I was at work but today I had the day off and I picked them up so buckle up, lets go for a ride! Apologies for all the pics being in one folder I did not have time to sort them!
---
#QUALITY **Louis Vuitton Silk Shirt** Overall great quality, although tags say Louis Vuitton, made in Japan Im not sure if thats correct but the silk is very nice and soft. Really impressed with this!*
**Red Givenchy tee** *OMG! Everything is perfect, how good is that distressing? I mean I really cant pick a fault with this except XL fits like an L but thats a minor.*
**Ivory Gucci tee** *Amazing quality from pirit, I didnt expect it to be this good as it was so cheap but I will definitely be flexing in this!*
**Ferragamo Slides** *Yeah fucking yeah bitch, Whos the daddy? Cheap as fuck and they are way more comfier than Gucci ones.*
**Tom Ford Henry Shades** *Never heard of Tom Ford shades before I came into this sub but as it makes my favourite fragrances I thought I would grab a pair seeing how everyone raves on about quality. Got them from AOOKO, quality is nice but they feel really light compared to my retail Rayban Clubmasters? Other than that good purchase!*
**Gucci Socks** *These arent all that great but theyre just socks Im not paying $95 for a pair of socks that will be fucked after 2 or 3 wears.*
**Versace Greca Shorts** *Only fault I can find is the medusa face, like, what the fuck is that? I compared it to retails so you guys can see how bad the medusa is! Other than that A1 sauce.*
**DSQUARED2 Shorts** *2nd pair of DS2 shorts Ive bought, superb quality for the price. Must cop!*
**Balmain Jeans (Light Blue Black pairs)** *These ones fit absolutely perfect and TTS, I wear a 30 waist which is what I ordered and they look feel great! Good quality denim not that stretch shit!*
**Balmain Jeans (Blue pair)** *Absolutely amazing in terms of quality, its a shame I will be selling these!*
**Chanel Soccer Jersey** *Probably my favourite pickup so far its a fantasy piece, quality is great for the price too! Bargain :)*
**Versace Medusa Nylon Backpack** *SNM Fam 1:1*
**Versace Velvet Hoodie** *Oh shit, my grail. Picked it up in the Versace store in Westfield and wanted it ever since I tried it on. This feels exactly the same, Soft as shit velvet! The medusa on the back is spot on. Thanks u/RepsJ for making me search for this.*
---
#SIZING **Louis Vuitton Silk Shirt** *TTS, for a tailored fit size down.*
**Red Givenchy tee** *SIZE UP*
**Ivory Gucci tee** *TTS*
**Ferragamo Slides** *TTS so comfy*
**Tom Ford Henry Shades** *Wicked fit, not sure about you big heads*
**Gucci Socks** *Quite small, wouldnt recommend if your bigger than size EU43*
**Versace Greca Shorts** *TTS*
**DSQUARED2 Shorts** *Size up*

**Balmain Jeans (Blue pair)** *Size down, twice!*
